WEBVTT

00:01:59.040 --> 00:01:59.760
Come, everyone.

00:02:00.640 --> 00:02:01.000
Please.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:01.640
Please, please.

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:02.159
Please.

00:02:07.359 --> 00:02:07.879
Careful.

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.000
Miss, are you all right?

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:19.560
What is this?

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:21.280
Don't touch it.

00:02:27.039 --> 00:02:27.840
It smells terrible.

00:02:28.199 --> 00:02:29.719
Is this sewage leaking?

00:02:29.840 --> 00:02:30.400
It stinks so much.

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:33.240
It really does.

00:02:34.199 --> 00:02:34.680
It reeks.

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.319
This isn't the smell of sewage.

00:02:36.639 --> 00:02:37.360
It's the smell of a corpse.

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:41.680
C-Corpse smell?

00:02:47.159 --> 00:02:48.199
A hand! A hand!

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:51.960
Young Master, this...

00:03:00.319 --> 00:03:01.240
It's Father.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:03.199
Manor Lord!

00:03:04.159 --> 00:03:04.800
Father!

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:06.599
Father! Miss!

00:03:06.800 --> 00:03:07.840
Are you sure this is the Manor Lord?

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:12.680
This ring is the All-Knowing Manor's heirloom.

00:03:12.800 --> 00:03:14.159
Only the Manor Lord can wear it.

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:15.680
And these clothes...

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.120
Miss made them herself for the Manor Lord's birthday.

00:03:19.240 --> 00:03:20.759
The last time we saw the Manor Lord,

00:03:20.919 --> 00:03:22.280
he was wearing this very outfit.

00:03:23.400 --> 00:03:24.479
Father!

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.039
Father!

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:45.280
Everyone.

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:47.319
My father once said

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:50.599
the Thousand Secrets Treasure is linked to this riddle.

00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:51.719
Thank you.

00:03:52.039 --> 00:03:52.759
Now,

00:03:53.479 --> 00:03:54.960
I suspect my father's murder

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:56.360
is also inescapably

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.639
linked to it.

00:03:58.240 --> 00:04:00.639
Where yellow clouds to the ninth heaven rise,

00:04:01.400 --> 00:04:03.560
The Court calls a water immortal to appear,

00:04:04.199 --> 00:04:06.000
The immortal points to the Book of Endless Life,

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:08.560
Its keeper crosses the river, leaving the mortal sphere.

00:04:09.680 --> 00:04:12.479
Did you find anything when examining the body?

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:14.280
Just now, while moving the body,

00:04:14.680 --> 00:04:15.680
I did a rough examination.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:17.160
The deceased

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.399
likely died over a month ago.

00:04:20.399 --> 00:04:22.000
Pierced through the chest; three fatal strikes.

00:04:22.480 --> 00:04:23.000
Furthermore,

00:04:24.879 --> 00:04:25.800
the head is missing.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:30.839
Could the Manor Lord have provoked an enemy?

00:04:31.519 --> 00:04:32.279
Is it

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:34.079
a vendetta?

00:04:34.199 --> 00:04:35.079
Then we must report this to the officials.

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:35.720
I'll go.

00:04:36.439 --> 00:04:37.120
Zhang Shan,

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.160
the miasma is too thick tonight.

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.000
Even if you've taken the antidote pill,

00:04:41.240 --> 00:04:42.639
you may not be able to make it out.

00:04:43.399 --> 00:04:45.920
To have this happen during a banquet...

00:04:46.959 --> 00:04:47.879
what rotten luck.

00:04:48.120 --> 00:04:48.800
Everyone,

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.240
I wish to stay with my father.

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:55.680
I was close friends with the Manor Lord.

00:04:56.279 --> 00:04:56.879
Young Master,

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:59.079
please let me accompany you.

00:05:18.399 --> 00:05:19.399
Missing for a month,

00:05:20.279 --> 00:05:21.800
without a single clue found.

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:23.680
The Metropolitan Governor found nothing,

00:05:24.399 --> 00:05:25.519
the Dali Temple found nothing.

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:28.879
Yet here at the All-Knowing Banquet,

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.399
the body just suddenly appears.

00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:33.000
It really is too coincidental.

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:35.399
Don't meddle in this.

00:05:35.959 --> 00:05:36.759
Get lost.

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:38.680
Lord Hua,

00:05:39.399 --> 00:05:40.439
please sheath your official blade.

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:42.600
I sincerely want to help you investigate the case.

00:05:55.920 --> 00:05:56.480
Wax.

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.639
First, seal the body in wax inside the statue,

00:06:00.079 --> 00:06:01.000
then hoist it up to the roof beam.

00:06:01.759 --> 00:06:03.319
Choosing this moment to let it fall...

00:06:04.040 --> 00:06:05.040
what exactly is the reason?

00:06:08.720 --> 00:06:09.639
Just playing tricks.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:10.720
Indeed.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.399
Young masters.

00:06:16.600 --> 00:06:18.279
May we see your name cards?

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:19.680
What do you want?

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:20.439
What do we want?

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:24.319
I'd say you two don't act like Jianghu folk.

00:06:24.959 --> 00:06:25.959
You look more...

00:06:26.439 --> 00:06:27.360
like you're from the government.

00:06:32.079 --> 00:06:33.439
What if I refuse?

00:06:34.079 --> 00:06:35.040
Refuse?

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.160
Gentlemen.

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:43.680
Let's talk this over calmly.

00:06:44.199 --> 00:06:47.160
I am Du Zhong, a traveling doctor.

00:06:53.000 --> 00:06:53.639
And this...

00:06:54.199 --> 00:06:56.000
is my apprentice, Ah Kun.

00:06:56.439 --> 00:06:58.519
He's had a bad temper since childhood.

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:00.279
Please forgive him, everyone.

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:03.920
So it's the Miracle Doctor Du Zhong!

00:07:04.920 --> 00:07:06.319
I've heard so much about you.

00:07:07.279 --> 00:07:08.920
Twenty taels, and I'll vouch for you.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:12.120
Everyone!

00:07:12.519 --> 00:07:13.240
I...

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:14.560
have met Du Zhong before.

00:07:17.759 --> 00:07:18.480
Two years ago,

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:20.040
I was seriously ill.

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.560
Thanks to our Miracle Doctor Du's prescription,

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:25.279
to think I'd meet my benefactor today!

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.240
A pleasure, a pleasure.

00:07:27.600 --> 00:07:28.639
Saving lives...

00:07:28.879 --> 00:07:29.560
is my duty.

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:30.639
Miracle Doctor! Miracle Doctor!

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:31.839
So it is Miracle Doctor Du.

00:07:32.399 --> 00:07:33.560
A pleasure, a pleasure.

00:07:34.759 --> 00:07:35.399
A pleasure.

00:07:35.600 --> 00:07:36.639
A pleasure, a pleasure.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:38.800
Why are you wearing shackles?

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:39.920
You are a criminal.

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:45.720
Ah Kun.

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.199
Explain it to them for your master.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:52.439
It's like this.

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:57.000
My master has been testing a new drug recently.

00:07:57.720 --> 00:07:58.439
Unfortunately,

00:07:58.639 --> 00:08:00.439
he was poisoned by the rare Netherworld Powder.

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:01.920
Whenever it flares up,

00:08:02.360 --> 00:08:03.319
he bites anyone he sees.

00:08:03.959 --> 00:08:04.600
Therefore,

00:08:05.399 --> 00:08:06.600
he took a pair of shackles

00:08:06.839 --> 00:08:07.959
and handcuffed himself.

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:09.199
By the way, Master,

00:08:10.240 --> 00:08:11.199
the time is almost up.

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:13.439
You're due for an attack, aren't you?

00:08:22.519 --> 00:08:23.040
Divine Physician

00:08:23.240 --> 00:08:24.560
An acquaintance! An acquaintance!

00:08:24.839 --> 00:08:25.839
Are you crazy?

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:28.319
Sorry, everyone.

00:08:28.560 --> 00:08:30.560
I'll take my master back to his room to rest.

00:08:33.960 --> 00:08:34.360
Disciple.

00:08:35.200 --> 00:08:35.679
Ah Kun.

00:08:36.559 --> 00:08:37.360
He's really crazy.

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:45.759
It happened so suddenly.

00:08:45.759 --> 00:08:46.799
I know I've offended you, My Lord.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.120
Please be the bigger person and forgive us.

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:48.759
Ye Li.

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:50.279
I don't care what methods you used...

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:51.840
...to make Lord Yin believe you can solve the case.

00:08:52.399 --> 00:08:53.159
But I advise you...

00:08:53.639 --> 00:08:54.679
...don't try to be too smart.

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:58.559
You can run for a while, but not forever.

00:08:59.120 --> 00:09:01.399
A life owed must eventually be paid.

00:09:01.639 --> 00:09:02.200
Lord Hua.

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:04.120
I truly want to help you investigate the case.

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:05.279
I don't need it.

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:09.039
The Lord of a martial arts sect goes missing.

00:09:09.639 --> 00:09:11.960
Lord Meng, the Metropolitan Governor, investigated personally.

00:09:13.120 --> 00:09:14.679
Only to be mysteriously killed.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:17.639
And I was identified as the killer by the Eunuch Faction.

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.159
The Manor Lord's body...

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.840
...suddenly appeared at his own manor's banquet.

00:09:22.360 --> 00:09:22.879
Lord Hua.

00:09:23.279 --> 00:09:24.960
Do you really think all this is a coincidence?

00:09:25.840 --> 00:09:27.559
It looks to me like someone did it on purpose.

00:09:30.600 --> 00:09:31.960
Lord Nine Thousand Years is with the Empress Dowager's faction.

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:33.399
They have always been at odds with the Crown Prince.

00:09:33.960 --> 00:09:35.200
Lord Meng and your Dali Temple...

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:36.799
...are all the Crown Prince's men.

00:09:37.440 --> 00:09:38.720
If I really killed Lord Meng...

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:39.879
...wouldn't that old castrated donkey...

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:42.080
...prefer to watch the Crown Prince's humiliation from afar?

00:09:42.759 --> 00:09:44.720
Why be in such a rush to sentence me to beheading?

00:09:45.039 --> 00:09:46.120
And send a trusted aide to supervise the execution?

00:09:46.919 --> 00:09:48.120
And bring trouble upon himself?

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:50.519
That is between you and the Eunuch Faction.

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:51.320
It has nothing to do with me.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.399
Stay here and behave yourself.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:54.240
Otherwise...

00:09:54.679 --> 00:09:56.480
...I can deliver that executioner's blow to you at any time.

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.360
Wasn't Lord Meng your teacher?

00:10:38.919 --> 00:10:39.399
Young Master.

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:41.000
I'm here to bring food.

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:45.240
Zhao Yun.

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:52.720
Xiao Bai.

00:10:54.840 --> 00:10:55.600
Stop hiding.

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:56.720
I saw it all.

00:11:07.799 --> 00:11:08.759
Since you are a Divine Physician...

00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:11.039
...why don't you treat your own wound?

00:11:11.879 --> 00:11:12.639
I'm not.

00:11:16.240 --> 00:11:17.279
Why are you so honest?

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:20.600
I just don't want to lie to you.

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:23.320
Then who are you?

00:11:25.080 --> 00:11:25.840
A prisoner.

00:11:27.360 --> 00:11:28.399
I mean your name.

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:31.720
My name is Ye Li.

00:11:32.159 --> 00:11:33.960
Ye as in willow leaf, Li as in propriety.

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:42.120
Why were you staring at me just now?

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:47.440
You look very much like a childhood friend of mine.

00:11:49.519 --> 00:11:51.840
Your way of getting close to someone is really cliché.

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:53.480
Alright.

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:54.720
Thank you.

00:11:55.720 --> 00:11:56.279
You must be hungry.

00:11:57.039 --> 00:11:57.840
Eat something, quickly.

00:12:06.000 --> 00:12:06.679
You are sick.

00:12:08.759 --> 00:12:09.320
Cold disease.

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:11.360
You cough whenever you catch a chill.

00:12:12.039 --> 00:12:13.840
It gets worse when it rains.

00:12:14.559 --> 00:12:15.399
Just feeling cold all over.

00:12:15.919 --> 00:12:16.600
It's nothing serious.

00:12:17.720 --> 00:12:18.600
In the Manor...

00:12:18.679 --> 00:12:20.759
...there's an Imperial Physician's prescription for cold disease.

00:12:21.000 --> 00:12:21.759
I'll go get it for you.

00:12:22.159 --> 00:12:22.960
An Imperial Palace prescription?

00:12:23.879 --> 00:12:25.679
The Manor has such good things?

00:12:26.679 --> 00:12:27.120
Of course.

00:12:27.519 --> 00:12:29.320
The Manor Lord's connections are everywhere.

00:12:29.399 --> 00:12:31.679
From imperial relatives to commoners.

00:12:32.240 --> 00:12:34.039
He knows all secrets.

00:12:34.039 --> 00:12:34.840
Hence, "All-Knowing".

00:12:35.120 --> 00:12:36.000
How could it lack a prescription?

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:41.200
Murder!

00:12:48.440 --> 00:12:49.720
Liu... Liu... Liu...

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:52.639
Master Liu is dead!